My Story

I have being opsest with the computer world since I was little kid I make a lot of experiments as a kid on how to program a machine , My first start learning about web grograming when I was 14 years old using some youtube tutoriels on HTML and CSS and JavaScript , after a while I stop doing coding to focus more on my school , but my passion never died about and I have being follow the evelousion of the tech all the time .

at the age of 15 my teacher of the tech have proposed to me to be one of the team that will make a robot for a school project because he saw in me the passion of the tech and programming , so we build a robot that throw a ball in the hole after folowing a black line in the ground , we used the Arduino Uno to program the robot , for the teacher maybe it was just a project but for me it was my first time starting to know about a real programing laguege (basics) . when I was 17 years old I get my baccalaureate (science phisique) at the school of ibn khaldoun bouznika .

and I went to Ista bouznika (IT development) for 2 years and during this two years I get my diplomat of specialist technician in IT development .
